create a container:
-----------------------------------------------
docker run -it --name con1 ubuntu /bin/bash
to enter exiesting container:
-----------------------------------------
docker exec -it con1 /bin/bash
to create custom image from docker file:
--------------------------------------------------
#vi dockerfile
# docker build -t myimg .
to create custom image of the container:
-----------------------------------------------------------------
#docker commit c10 1aug2024img
this command will create a custom image of the container c10 with a namw 1aug2024img.

